    "description": "Yuzu is the secret weapon for this pumped up peppercorn sauce. Drizzle over pan-fried chicken breast and serve with togarashi potatoes and a side of edamame for an unbeatable 10 minute meal. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
